                                                "OldText" : {
                                                   "handle" : "h69c16c7eg062eg4307ga168g583e5bdb649a",
                                                   "type" : 28, "value" : "Poison's not my style. Nor's becoming a mind flayer. We'll have to make sure to steer clear of both eventualities.",
                                                   "version" : 1
                                                },
                                                "TagText" : {
                                                   "handle" : "he91efb9ega9f9g4846g854ag3ffcbe3e371f",
                                                   "type" : 28, "value" : "Standard goblin raiding party. Question is, was it plunder they wanted  - or did they seek something more?",
